trans-unit.source: Represents a collection of <see cref="T:System.Windows.Documents.Block" /> elements.
trans-unit.target: Representa uma coleção de elementos <see cref="T:System.Windows.Documents.Block" />.

trans-unit.source: <see cref="T:System.Windows.Documents.BlockCollection" /> defines the allowable child content of the <see cref="T:System.Windows.Documents.FlowDocument" />, <see cref="T:System.Windows.Documents.Section" />, <see cref="T:System.Windows.Documents.ListItem" />, <see cref="T:System.Windows.Documents.TableCell" />, <see cref="T:System.Windows.Documents.Floater" />, and <see cref="T:System.Windows.Documents.Figure" /> elements.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="T:System.Windows.Documents.BlockCollection" /> define o conteúdo filho permitido dos elementos <see cref="T:System.Windows.Documents.FlowDocument" />, <see cref="T:System.Windows.Documents.Section" />, <see cref="T:System.Windows.Documents.ListItem" />, <see cref="T:System.Windows.Documents.TableCell" />, <see cref="T:System.Windows.Documents.Floater" /> e <see cref="T:System.Windows.Documents.Figure" />.

trans-unit.source: <xref:System.Windows.Documents.BlockCollection> creation is only permitted inside an element that owns a <xref:System.Windows.Documents.BlockCollection>, such as a <xref:System.Windows.Documents.FlowDocument> or <xref:System.Windows.Documents.TextElement>.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Windows.Documents.BlockCollection> criação só é permitida dentro de um elemento que possui um <xref:System.Windows.Documents.BlockCollection>, como um <xref:System.Windows.Documents.FlowDocument> ou <xref:System.Windows.Documents.TextElement>.

trans-unit.source: As such, a <xref:System.Windows.Documents.BlockCollection> cannot be instantiated directly and has no default or overloaded constructor.
trans-unit.target: Como tal, um <xref:System.Windows.Documents.BlockCollection> não pode ser instanciado diretamente e não possui padrão ou sobrecarregado construtor.

trans-unit.source: Gets the first <see cref="T:System.Windows.Documents.Block" /> element within this instance of <see cref="T:System.Windows.Documents.BlockCollection" />.
trans-unit.target: Obtém o primeiro elemento de <see cref="T:System.Windows.Documents.Block" /> dentro desta instância de <see cref="T:System.Windows.Documents.BlockCollection" />.

trans-unit.source: The first <see cref="T:System.Windows.Documents.Block" /> element in the <see cref="T:System.Windows.Documents.BlockCollection" />.
Gets the last <see cref="T:System.Windows.Documents.Block" /> element within this instance of <see cref="T:System.Windows.Documents.BlockCollection" />.
trans-unit.target: Obtém o último elemento de <see cref="T:System.Windows.Documents.Block" /> dentro desta instância de <see cref="T:System.Windows.Documents.BlockCollection" />.

trans-unit.source: The last <see cref="T:System.Windows.Documents.Block" /> element in the <see cref="T:System.Windows.Documents.BlockCollection" />.
